• Unlimited downloads of Unsolved Papers for Paid and Unpaid users.
• Unlimited sharing of Unsolved Papers.

• Smallest size of app in this category.

• Added NEET 2021 Solved and Unsolved Paper.
• Added an option to Bookmark Pages in each and every Paper.
